description: Disables the APNs channel for an application and deletes any existing settings for the channel.

parameters.name: ApplicationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the application. This identifier is displayed as the Project ID on the Amazon Pinpoint console.

nested_items.name: APNSChannelResponse
nested_items.description: Provides information about the status and settings of the APNs (Apple Push Notification service) channel for an application.

nested_items.name: ApplicationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the application that the APNs channel applies to.

nested_items.name: CreationDate
nested_items.description: The date and time when the APNs channel was enabled.

nested_items.name: DefaultAuthenticationMethod
nested_items.description: The default authentication method that Amazon Pinpoint uses to authenticate with APNs for this channel, key or certificate.

nested_items.name: Enabled
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the APNs channel is enabled for the application.

nested_items.name: HasCredential
nested_items.description: (Not used) This property is retained only for backward compatibility.

nested_items.name: HasTokenKey
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the APNs channel is configured to communicate with APNs by using APNs tokens. To provide an authentication key for APNs tokens, set the TokenKey property of the channel.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: (Deprecated) An identifier for the APNs channel. This property is retained only for backward compatibility.

nested_items.name: IsArchived
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the APNs channel is archived.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedBy
nested_items.description: The user who last modified the APNs channel.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedDate
nested_items.description: The date and time when the APNs channel was last modified.

nested_items.name: Platform
nested_items.description: The type of messaging or notification platform for the channel. For the APNs channel, this value is APNS.

nested_items.name: Version
nested_items.description: The current version of the APNs channel.
